title: (Fri Full Show) Friday Morning Conversation with Parker McCollum and Performance + Amy Movers Showed Up Under the Influence + We Talk To Ryan Reynolds
itunes:title: (Fri Full Show) Friday Morning Conversation with Parker McCollum and Performance + Amy Movers Showed Up Under the Influence + We Talk To Ryan Reynolds
description:
Parker McCollum stops by to talk about his big ACM win, getting married at the end of the month and performs his song “To Be Loved By You”. Bobby also tries out a new parody with Parker. Amy says she had someone come move something really heavy in her house…the only problem is that they showed up visibly impaired. Should she have called to report them? We talk to Ryan Reynolds about his new movie on Netflix! Plus Easy Trivia, Fun Fact Friday and more Friday fun!
